    <item>
      <title>南非大选前预算的赢家和输家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/winners-and-losers-in-south-africa-s-pre-election-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非在预算方面取得了明显的胜利——距离关键选举还有几个月——但通过针对吸烟者和饮酒者而不是根据通货膨胀调整所得税等级，从纳税人身上榨取了更多收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/winners-and-losers-in-south-africa-s-pre-election-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 12:06:50 GMT</pubDate>
