      <title>南非寻求黄金，利用储备遏制失控的债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/south-africa-goes-for-gold-taps-reserves-to-curb-runaway-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[资金短缺的南非财政部长伊诺克·戈东瓦纳 (Enoch Godongwana) 利用该国的黄金和外汇储备来稳定其令人垂涎的债务，同时在关键的选举年增加教师、护士和福利方面的支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/south-africa-goes-for-gold-taps-reserves-to-curb-runaway-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 12:06:16 GMT</pubDate>
